Bruce McRae https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bruce_McRae 0 Bruce McRae (January 15, 1867, India - May 7, 1927 City Island, New York) was an American stage and early silent film actor. He was the nephew of actor Sir Charles Wyndham. Bruce_McRae ( January_15_,_1867 , India - May_7_,_1927_City_Island , New_York ) was an_American_stage and early_silent_film_actor .
